Launch Explorations for Data Cloud with a Single Click

Analyze and surface customer engagement patterns from Data Cloud records without switching to Analytics Studio. With Direct Data for Data Cloud, you can explore calculated insights, data lake objects, and data models from the record page. Review, profile, and trend data in tables and charts, or run queries on Data Cloud right in their business workflow.

Let's say you created a calculated insight on product clusters. To review spending by product categories:

Click Explore in Analytics.
Select Funnel (1).
Aggregate data by amount spent (2).
Group data by product subcategory (3).
Switch to Analytics Studio (4).
title: Launch Explorations for Data Cloud with CRM Analytics
